      <title>quantum field theory</title>
      <link href="/2022/06/22/quantum-field-theory/"/>
      <url>/2022/06/22/quantum-field-theory/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Feynman-Parameter"><a href="#Feynman-Parameter" class="headerlink" title="Feynman Parameter"></a>Feynman Parameter</h2><p>$<br>{\pi ^2}\int_0^1 \frac{ \rm dx  }{ \sqrt {(a^2x + b^2)(1 - x)} }   = \frac{ 2\pi ^2 }{a}arcsin\left( \frac{a}{ \sqrt { {a^2} + {b^2} } } \right)<br>$<br>证明：</p><blockquote><p>首先利用：<br>对$k$的全空间积分，平移$\vec k$结果不变，积分一次得到：<br>$\int_{ - \infty }^\infty  {\frac{ {\rm d ^3}k }{\left( {\vec k + \vec a} \right)}^2}(k^2 + b^2)  = {\pi ^2}\int_0^1 \frac{\rm{dx}}{\sqrt \Delta  } $<br>将$\Delta$显式写出$\Delta  = (a^2x + b^2)(1 - x)$：<br>再积分一次得到：<br>$<br>{\pi ^2}\int_0^1 \frac{ \rm dx  }{ \sqrt {(a^2x + b^2)(1 - x)} }   = \frac{ 2\pi ^2 }{a}arcsin\left( \frac{a}{ \sqrt { {a^2} + {b^2} } } \right)<br>$<br>这样我们就证明了这个结果 Q.E.D.</p></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
      
